Author: Sea_Plane
Text: I cannot even think about seroquel without shivering with fear.  Never again.

Author: 2ndtoLastUnicorn
Text: Me too!! Isnt it SO FUN to know you were rocking it and then just... stopped.   Sorry, I am just so disappointed in myself and this really hit the nail on the head. Went from underweight to overweight in one shitty year. But we did it before! There's hope!
